S-ToDo.text:
Hm...
I know!  We should build a house!

Well, YOU should build a house.

replies.text: Aw come on, why do I have to do it?
Why do we need a house?

S-Everyone.text:
Oh, I wouldn't know.

They were here one day, and gone the next.

I didn't keep track of humanity's affairs, what with my being a deer.

replies.text: I feel like you know more than you're letting on.
You are clearly not a regular deer.

Home.text:
Well, this is sufficiently tragic.

That's life, I suppose.

replies.text: So with that taken care of, what should we do now?
Any more chores you're going to have me do?

TeaTime.text:
[give tea]I thought the funeral was going to be a miserable affair, but this was quite enjoyable!

What a lovely way to send everyone off.

Not with tears or sorrow, but a peaceful little tea party.

replies.text: So what should we do now?

SD-Hands.text:
Uh

Because I don't have hands?
